687
01:00:33,360 --> 01:00:35,360
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, Thomas, krenimo s tobom.

688
01:00:35,519 --> 01:00:36,880
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim, čuješ to cijelo vrijeme.

689
01:00:36,960 --> 01:00:38,559
[SPEAKER_02] Kako radim preporuke??

690
